  "html": "<h1>Applies to</h1>\n  <ul>\n    <li>PCI DSS Requirement 7.1.2 </li>\n    <li>PCI DSS Requirement 7.1.3 </li>\n    <li>PCI DSS Requirement 7.2.2</li>\n  </ul>\n  <h1>What to Do</h1>\n  <p>Assign access privileges based on job functions.</p>\n  <h1>Why</h1>\n  <p>Assigning data access privileges based on job functions ensures that employees can work but cannot wage insider attacks.</p>\n  <h1>How</h1>\n  <p>Identify the job functions of each employee. Identify the data access required for each employee. Define the data access privileges for each employee based on job responsibilities.&amp;nbsp; Have the management review and authorize the data access privilege specifications.\n Once approved, implement the data access control systems. Attach the access authorization documents to the network documentation.</p>"
